{"tid":463290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聖瑪加利女書院遭黑客入侵","createTime":"2017-11-09T10:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T11:15:16.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb93ff1aac84a93db0e741207e3d76e67d77b57","tid":463290,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"本港3日內發生兩宗黑客入侵事件，繼縱橫遊旅行社後，沙田大圍聖瑪加利女書院昨晚亦發現校內一個中央伺服器被人入侵，並發現一段來自payfordecrypt1@qq.com的可疑訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。學校已就事件通知教育局，並同時啟動危機處理小組跟進事件；事故未為校方日常運作帶來影響。警方將案暫列作「不誠實使用電腦」案，交由沙田警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20171109/_2017110910404499466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20171109%2F_2017110910404499466.jpg&h=497cbc8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，黑客並沒有向學校勒索。而記者今早到學校了解事件，校方指因校長需要上課，故不會對事件作回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1060844/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1060844%2F&d=qFMizAWkK58qCn8pkwBdHS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d3b27105\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1060844%2F&h=1a2374d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1060844/</a>"},{"pid":"bd4d4716508d6534ef3c762363b2cce548e76f41","tid":463290,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"Qq <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badbd73c4fde8e7d1a3683893cf1ade239c59ada","tid":463290,"uid":34223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:15:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://qq.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqq.com&d=qFMizAWkK58qCn8pkwBdHS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d9d6c8df\